    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80e8-97b1-d1bf863c36f5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper presents a recommender for university specialization. This is an important problem to address because choosing a major is very relevant for students. The recommender uses Collaborative Filtering and its acccuracy was assessed with K-Fold Cross-Validation. Model is reported to work well. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
